{"tid":696113,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有食過彩ge 入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-06-09T19:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T08:41:14.000Z","uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3ffdbbd9379ff0895b4c40d4ac3ed972d774794","tid":696113,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:08:57.000Z","msg":"話說，一直都幾鐘意食拉麵<br />\n之前成日睇連登啲飲食台，好多人都好推薦彩呢間沾麵鋪<br />\n咁近呢幾日就去咗元朗間鋪食啦<br />\n一入到去好有日本傳統拉麵店feel <br />\n有個師傅係到整野食，大家一排排咁坐<br />\n但係一入去就聞到勁大浸腥味，唔太習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐低咗之後，我都好快咁叫咗啲野食<br />\n負責落單個女仔啲態度真係閪撚到好明顯<br />\n好多外國人成日都投訴香港服務態度唔好<br />\n作為一個土生土長嘅香港人，我覺得好多餐廳侍應嘅態度都可以<br />\n但係果日去到個女仔態度真係好難頂<br />\n咁我同朋友以為做錯咗啲唔禮貌嘅事得罪咗佢啦<br />\n落野、遞水果時都有講哂唔該咁<br />\n點知都仲係咁閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能佢嚟m燥咗啲咩，我都明白可能真係好辛苦嘅<br />\n但係做得侍應，你嘅一舉一動、反應都會影響到個客<br />\n果餐搞到我同我朋友都唔太敢係入面傾計（細細聲傾）<br />\n之後，佢送啲沾麵嚟啦，碗湯都勁濃腥味，可能對其他人而言係鮮味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我就食唔太慣喇<br />\n但有樣野幾抵讚，佢地啲湯料好足，啲麵餅勁大份<br />\n一開始預咗食拉麵可能會唔太飽，所以追加咗個麵底<br />\n點知一個麵底已經食到好飽，最後死頂唔想浪費野食先食哂第二份麵<br />\n啲湯料有蛋有筍，叉燒正常size ，價錢同出面連鎖拉麵鋪略平<br />\n如果唔係啲湯勁腥同個女staff ge 態度<br />\n應該都會成日去<br />\n最後補番句：打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9513f621331437ab5a9733833202ef2e1adfbf4e","tid":696113,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb86805fa6b1f4570910fefea40687a0b74cce40","tid":696113,"uid":45007,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/10/032312_3d9c8033943cdb71100e4951166d748f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F10%2F032312_3d9c8033943cdb71100e4951166d748f.png&h=88d85d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n閣下形容令我想起呢碗拉面"},{"pid":"6377ee7fdf9fefbca1395fbb7488baaf6a237a52","tid":696113,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"西環果間彩都係有好撚臭既味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489b816150e1f315edc74672e8faea3c4706dcbc","tid":696113,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"老闆喺元朗開返舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無記錯上年元朗間舖清咗盤，老闆搬咗去西環<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=304067573349858&amp;id=211878955902054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D304067573349858%26id%3D211878955902054&d=zGVRLTQBPH4w8ArbeQXnJp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=4c08cb68\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=304067573349858&amp;id=211878955902054</a><br />\n<br />\n單嘢上咗連登仲backup埋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/225277/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/225277/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d776034bc06b69d6b54e294fdbc07285c2150df4","tid":696113,"uid":11760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6377ee7fdf9fefbca1395fbb7488baaf6a237a52","tid":696113,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:47:11.000Z","msg":"西環果間彩都係有好撚臭既味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"臭筍味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}